{"tid":1521542,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"可以引入# hashtags？","createTime":"2019-08-31T09:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T13:41:45.000Z","uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d2bfea6492ccfa896052c183a5059e8a4f63da33","tid":1521542,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T09:07:55.000Z","msg":"好似twitter咁，加入hashtag<br />\n例如有求del post 既可以內文加#連仔 方便盡快處理<br />\n有活動又可以組織hashtag，方便lihkg 散播同埋其他媒體散播<br />\n一㩒落個tag就啟動類似搜尋既功能，sort返晒所有有落過同一個tag嘅po同comment。hashtag大小寫不影響。<br />\n<br />\n連尼住辛苦你了！光復香港！時代革命！"},{"pid":"a4cfff7c96d1ddb7c34921c17c4ebc43c438672f","tid":1521542,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"佢本身個search都唔係好用,仲加tag?<br />\n你要佢分返開search文章/用戶名同tag先啦"},{"pid":"12ce04054020eeefa14b8f04b4f93114412409ad","tid":1521542,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4cfff7c96d1ddb7c34921c17c4ebc43c438672f","tid":1521542,"uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"佢本身個search都唔係好用,仲加tag?<br />\n你要佢分返開search文章/用戶名同tag先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"都係。同埋第二個建議係網頁版加password，每次開連登都要打passcode，好似手機版咁"}]}